All Classes

Class Description
Application
The main class for KUERES.
BaseController<E extends BaseEntity<E>,​R extends BaseRepository<E>,​S extends BaseService<E,​R>>
The BaseController provides basic CRUD functionality for a BaseEntity.
BaseEntity<E extends BaseEntity<E>>
The BaseEntity provides each entity with a unique identifier.
BaseRepository<E extends BaseEntity<E>>
The BaseRepository provides repository functionality for a BaseEntity that is needed for the rest of the kueres.base package.
BaseService<E extends BaseEntity<E>,​R extends BaseRepository<E>>
The BaseService provides the services needed by a BaseController.
DefaultFileSystemRepository
The default implementation of the FileSystemRepository interface.
DefaultLocationService
The default implementation of the location service.
EntitySpecification<E extends BaseEntity<E>>
Construct a Predicate from search criteria.
ErrorController
Mask outgoing errors.
EventConsumer
The EventConsumer receives all events and distributes them to EventSubscribers.
EventController
The EventController provides API functions for EventEntities.
EventEntity
The EventEntity is representation of events from the eventbus.
EventRepository
The repository for EventEntities.
EventService
The EventService provides services needed by the EventController.
EventSubscriber
Super class for all classes that want to receive events.
EventType
All event types used by the eventbus.
FileSystemRepository
An interface for all functions needed by the media system that interact with storage.
KeycloakConfiguration
Configuration for the connection between the Spring Boot server and the Keycloak service.
KueresConfigurationProperties
Provide all custom configuration options that can be set in application.properties.
LocationService
An interface for all functions provided by the location service.
MediaController
The MediaController provides all API functions related to media.
MediaEntity
A MediaEntity contains data about a file.
MediaRepository
The repository for MediaEntities.
MediaService
The MediaService provides services needed by the MediaController.
OnMessageExecutor
This executor is used to customize how events are distributed to EventSubscribers.
RabbitMQConfiguration
Configuration for the connection between the Spring Boot server and the RabbitMQ service.
ReceiveMessageExecutor
This executor is used to customize how events are logged.
SearchCriteria
The class representation of a search criteria.
SearchOperation
A list of all supported search/filter operations and their symbols.
SortBuilder
The SortBuilder constructs Spring Sort objects used for sorting repository requests.
Utility
Provides utility functions like logging.
